Zverev will begin his campaign in Rome against Camilo Ugo Carabelli or a qualifier/lucky loser. He is seeded to face Alcaraz in a blockbuster semi-final clash.
“I feel confident here," Zverev added. "I really like the place, so I hope I can play as well as last year and win a lot of matches.”





